data.text:
The Many Loves of Dobie Gillis Caper at the Bijou

In order to obtain enough money to impress Thalia on their prom date, Dobie conspires with his beatnik friend Maynard to rig a raffle at the local movie theater.

The Many Loves of Dobie Gillis The Best Dressed Man

Dobie tries to impress Thalia by dressing as nicely as the rich Milton Armitage. A frustrated Milton doesn't know that Dobie is borrowing his duds from a local tailor.

The Many Loves of Dobie Gillis Love Is a Science

Thalia urges Dobie to become a doctor, but he meets Zelda Gilroy and learns about the scientific concept of propinquity, the psychological tendency for people to form relationships with those whom they encounter often.

The Many Loves of Dobie Gillis The Right Triangle

Dobie's rarely seen older brother advises him to try to gain sympathy from a new girl in school by bemoaning his affair with a married older woman, but this causes the girl to conclude that Dobie is involved with their math teacher, Mrs. Adams.

The Many Loves of Dobie Gillis Dobie Gillis: Boy Actor

Dobie auditions for the school play in order to impress a girl, but discovers that he is up against Milton to be leading man.

The Many Loves of Dobie Gillis Room at the Bottom

Thalia talks Dobie's parents into sending him to Willoughby, a local prep school. He doesn't attend, but Mr. Gillis has a dream in which he imagines Dobie with a rich roommate.

The Many Loves of Dobie Gillis The Power of Positive Thinking

In order to win Thaila from Chatsworth Osborne Jr., Dobie reads a book on mental power so he can be the dominating man that Thalia wants.

The Many Loves of Dobie Gillis Live Alone and Like It

Dobie and Maynard strike out on their own.

The Many Loves of Dobie Gillis Where There's a Will

Herbert balks at signing his will.

The Many Loves of Dobie Gillis Put Your Feet in Our Hands

For love, Dobie works in a shoe shop.

The Many Loves of Dobie Gillis Dobie Goes Beatnik

Thelonious Monk comes to town and invites Maynard to sit in on bongos; but Herbert needs a favor that will require Dobie and Maynard to switch identities.

The Many Loves of Dobie Gillis Around My Room in 80 Days

Dobie tries to prevent a classmate from dropping out.

The Many Loves of Dobie Gillis Like Mother, Like Daughter, Like Wow

Wini thinks a widow is after Herbert.

The Many Loves of Dobie Gillis Like Father, Like Son, Like Trouble

Dobie and Maynard masquerade as a war hero and aide.
